{"article_id":"zOrIZJggYXzxzBQ9","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Congressional Republicans are looking to revive legislation","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"that could give a deportation reprieve to thousands of illegal immigrants","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"who came to the U.S. as children ,","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"in turn easing the pressure on President Trump","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"as he faces a deadline","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to decide the fate of a related Obama-era program .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Sen. Thom Tillis , R-N.C. , is leading the charge on a conservative version of the so-called Dream Act .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"The talks come","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"as Trump prepares to announce","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"whether he ' ll keep the Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"( DACA )","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"program -","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"which was former President Barack Obama ' s unilateral , executive-action version of Dream Act legislation .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The timing for a Trump announcement has been fluid .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"In the most recent guidance , White House Press Secretary Sarah Sanders said","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"the decision will be made next Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"Trump initially had said","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"the call could come as early as Friday or this weekend ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"without going into detail .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"Asked if ' Dreamers , ' or those affected by the policy , should be worried ,","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Trump told reporters :","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"`` We love Dreamers .","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"We love everybody . ''","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"One official told earlier","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"that Trump ultimately is expected to end DACA ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"while allowing those in the country","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"who qualified under the program","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"to stay","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"until their work permits expire .","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Such a move would infuriate Democrats","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"- as well as some moderate Republicans .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"However , if lawmakers can draft legislation","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that accomplishes similar goals ,","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"it could give Trump some leeway","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"to end DACA","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"without significant impact .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"A senior administration official suggested Friday","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"that the onus was back on Congress","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"to pursue a legislative solution .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"`` Congress has to do this , \"","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"the official told .","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"Some Republicans support the goals of Obama ' s DACA","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"but think","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"the former president committed an overreach","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"by doing it through executive action .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Tillis ' office pointed to this distinction","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"in describing his legislative effort .","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"\" Regardless of the policy itself , DACA is an executive overreach","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"that sets immigration policy through executive order instead of the proper channel-legislation , \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Tillis spokesman Daniel Keylin told .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"\" It ' s the responsibility of Congress , not the President to offer a long-term legislative fix . \"","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Congress has been considering legislation","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"to shield young illegal immigrants from deportation","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"for years ,","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"dating back to the George W. Bush administration .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Lawmakers tried again to pass a bill during the Obama administration ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"but couldn ' t muster the votes","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"amid flagging Republican support .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"The Obama administration announced the DACA policy in 2012 .","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"According to Keylin ,","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Tillis will be working with Republicans on \" conservative legislation \"","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"to address the \" long-term uncertainty \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"undocumented minors face .","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Kelyin told","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that they needed to create a \" fair but rigorous process \" for legal status ,","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"requiring individuals 18 or older to either be \" employed ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"pursue post-secondary education ,","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"or serve in the Armed Forces . \"","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"While the legislation is still being drafted ,","depth":6},{"id":69,"text":"McClatchy reported","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"that Tillis ' bill is expected to be similar to one","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"introduced by Rep. Carlos Curbelo , R-Fla.","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Curbelo ' s bill , the \" Recognizing America ' s Children Act , \" would offer an eventual path to U.S. citizenship to immigrants","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"who entered illegally before Jan. 1 , 2012","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"and were 16 years old or younger ,","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"according to the Miami Herald .","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"\" The White House has sent a very strong message","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"by preserving the executive order","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"that protects these young people , \"","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Curbelo said in an interview with the Miami Herald in March .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"\" We know","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"that they ' ve been very aggressive","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"when it comes to immigration policy ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"so it certainly stands out that they have left the DACA executive order untouched . \"","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"On Friday , House Speaker Paul Ryan , R-Wis. , said","depth":6},{"id":85,"text":"he supported a legislative solution","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"to protect undocumented minors ,","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"but also urged the president to reconsider scrapping DACA .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"`` I actually do n't think","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"he should do that","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"and I believe","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"that this is something","depth":11},{"id":92,"text":"that Congress has to fix , ''","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"Ryan said on radio station WCLO in Janesville , Wis. , Friday .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"`` President Obama did not have a legislative authority","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"to do what he did . ''","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Ryan added :","depth":7},{"id":97,"text":"`` There are people","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"who are in limbo .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"These are kids","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"who know no other country ,","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"who were brought here by their parents","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"and do n't know another home .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"And so I really do believe","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"that there needs to be a legislative solution . ''","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"Sen. Orrin Hatch , R-Utah , also weighed in on the issue ,","depth":6},{"id":106,"text":"calling on the president to halt rescinding DACA ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"it would \" further complicate a system in serious need of permanent , legislative solution . \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Hatch added","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"that the \" solution must come from Congress , \"","depth":7},{"id":111,"text":"and that he will be working with colleagues and the administration","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"to pass \" meaningful immigration reform \"","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"and provide a \" workable path forward for the Dreamer population . \"","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Then-candidate Trump promised to terminate DACA during the 2016 presidential campaign ,","depth":3},{"id":115,"text":"but since taking office","depth":4},{"id":116,"text":"has weighed whether to preserve components of it .","depth":4},{"id":117,"text":"Looming in the background is the threat of potential legal action by state attorneys general","depth":4},{"id":118,"text":"led by Texas Attorney General Ken Paxton and nine other AGs","depth":5},{"id":119,"text":"who oppose DACA .","depth":5},{"id":120,"text":"Paxton said Thursday","depth":4},{"id":121,"text":"that his office would stick to a previously determined Sept. 5 deadline","depth":5},{"id":122,"text":"set by officials from Texas for a decision .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":245,"left":236,"right":244,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":173,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":145,"right":172,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":145,"left":129,"right":144,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":128,"right":6,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":125,"right":127,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":0,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":124,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":3,"right":126,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":134,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":7,"right":133,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":8,"right":132,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":132,"left":131,"right":12,"